    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shiver is a survival horror game in which a sudden blizzard has enveloped your town, but this isn’t an ordinary storm. Reality itself seems to unravel as you navigate a frozen hellscape to find your missing sister – all while defending yourself not only from horrors beyond our understanding but nature itself. Solve environmental puzzles, combat ice-covered nightmares, and attempt to uncover the mysteries that lie at the eye of the storm, but most importantly… survive. <br><br><strong>Navigate harsh weather</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monsters aren’t the only dangers in Shiver… The weather and inhospitable environments require careful preparation if you hope to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/150b14f8c8fb5863e9db3dd31bba1c22.poster.avif?t=1734395460\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/150b14f8c8fb5863e9db3dd31bba1c22.webm?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/150b14f8c8fb5863e9db3dd31bba1c22.mp4?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience a deep and emotional narrative</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Hannah, a young woman trapped in the middle of a freak blizzard trying to find her lost sister and get her to safety. Where have these creatures come from and what other mysteries will you discover? What fears would you face to save your family?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/01a02170a91bebc1bebd860381d62fea.poster.avif?t=1734395460\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/01a02170a91bebc1bebd860381d62fea.webm?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/01a02170a91bebc1bebd860381d62fea.mp4?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face abhorrent monsters throughout your journey</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use melee weapons and various firearms to combat the horrifying creatures that seem to come from the ice itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/38fbf289ff0c161a183adb577484834a.poster.avif?t=1734395460\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/38fbf289ff0c161a183adb577484834a.webm?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/38fbf289ff0c161a183adb577484834a.mp4?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <strong>3rd Person Camera</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate beautiful but terrifying landscapes, caverns, buildings and more from a modern over-the-shoulder view. Immerse yourself in the world of <strong>Shiver</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/b844f5157616f734cfb370a9630cc695.poster.avif?t=1734395460\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/b844f5157616f734cfb370a9630cc695.webm?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/b844f5157616f734cfb370a9630cc695.mp4?t=1734395460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
